# Component & Layout Rules

These components are **shared and considered stable**. Reuse them as-is.
Do not restyle, restructure, or "improve" them as a side effect of an
unrelated task. Only change them when the user explicitly asks, and only the
specific thing they ask for — never bundle in extra tweaks.

